Date: Thu, 2 Jul 2026 04:26:55 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 13/22] Add TermSurf crash callbacks

WebContent took the stage,
Then exited with flair.
Girlbat caught the curtain fall,
And filed a crash report there.
---
